## рЯЫ°пЄП Z Bot Moderation

CyberGuard Pro includes a powerful built-in moderation module (**Z Bot**) for Telegram group management.

### How It Works
Every message in the group goes through a multi-layer detection pipeline:

```
Message вЖТ Unicode Normalizer вЖТ Keyword Scorer вЖТ Domain Checker вЖТ Verdict вЖТ Action
```

### Scoring System
| Score | Verdict | Action |
|-------|---------|--------|
| 0вАУ39 | рЯЯҐ SAFE | No action |
| 40вАУ69 | рЯЯ° SUSPICIOUS | Warning issued |
| 70вАУ99 | рЯЯ† HIGH RISK | Message deleted + warning |
| 100+ | рЯФі DANGER | Message deleted + warning |

After **3 warnings** вЖТ user is **automatically banned**.

### Bypass Detection
Z Bot normalizes Unicode tricks spammers use to evade filters:
- Cyrillic/Greek lookalike characters (e.g. `—Хex` вЖТ `sex`)
- Invisible/zero-width characters
- Emoji flag encoding (e.g. рЯЗЄрЯЗ™рЯЗљ вЖТ `sex`)
- Fancy math/bold fonts

### Admin Commands
| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `/zban` | Ban a user |
| `/zunban` | Unban a user |
| `/zmute` | Mute a user |
| `/zunmute` | Unmute a user |
| `/zwarn` | Manually warn a user |
| `/warnings` | View warnings for a user |
| `/clearwarnings` | Clear all warnings for a user |
| `/rules` | Show group rules |

### Creator-Only Commands
| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `/zlogs` | Last 10 spam detections |
| `/zdebug <text>` | Test normalizer + scorer live |
| `/zstats` | Global bot statistics |
| `/zblacklist` | View/add/remove blacklisted domains |
| `/zwhitelist` | View/add/remove whitelisted domains |
| `/zmaintenance` | Toggle maintenance mode |
| `/zupdate` | Show bot version info |

